		    <h4 data-mce-style="padding-left: 30px;"><strong>1. Nguy&ecirc;n t&#7855;c chung</strong></h4>
		    <p>&#272;&oacute;n &#273;&#7847;u xu th&#7871; th&#7883; tr&#432;&#7901;ng, H&#7843;i Linh l&agrave; nh&atilde;n h&agrave;ng ti&ecirc;n phong trong ng&agrave;nh h&agrave;ng ti&ecirc;u d&ugrave;ng v&#7873; x&acirc;y d&#7921;ng v&agrave; ph&aacute;t tri&#7875;n k&ecirc;nh th&#432;&#417;ng m&#7841;i &#273;i&#7879;n t&#7917;, nh&#7857;m gi&uacute;p t&#259;ng &#273;&#7897; ph&#7911; s&oacute;ng c&#7911;a th&#432;&#417;ng hi&#7879;u s&#7843;n ph&#7849;m s&#7843;n xu&#7845;t b&#7903;i H&#7843;i Linh v&agrave; ph&aacute;t tri&#7875;n t&#7845;t c&#7843; c&aacute;c k&ecirc;nh b&aacute;n h&agrave;ng, gi&uacute;p kh&aacute;ch h&agrave;ng c&oacute; th&#7875; th&#7921;c hi&#7879;n h&agrave;nh vi mua h&agrave;ng m&#7885;i l&uacute;c m&#7885;i n&#417;i.</p>
		    <p>Website TM&#272;T dochoihailinh.vn do c&#7911;a &ocirc;ng L&ecirc; H&#7843;i Linh l&agrave;m ch&#7911; s&#7903; h&#7919;u. Th&agrave;nh vi&ecirc;n tr&ecirc;n Website TM&#272;T dochoihailinh.vn l&agrave; c&aacute;c th&#432;&#417;ng nh&acirc;n, t&#7893; ch&#7913;c, c&aacute; nh&acirc;n c&oacute; ho&#7841;t &#273;&#7897;ng th&#432;&#417;ng m&#7841;i h&#7907;p ph&aacute;p &#273;&#432;&#7907;c trangdai.com.vn ch&iacute;nh th&#7913;c c&ocirc;ng nh&#7853;n v&agrave; &#273;&#432;&#7907;c ph&eacute;p s&#7917; d&#7909;ng d&#7883;ch v&#7909; do Website TM&#272;T dochoihailinh.vn v&agrave; ng&#432;&#7901;i b&aacute;n/nh&agrave; cung c&#7845;p cung &#7913;ng d&#7883;ch v&#7909; mua b&aacute;n h&agrave;ng h&oacute;a &#273;&#7891; ch&#417;i tr&#7867; em.</p>
		    <h4 data-mce-style="padding-left: 30px;"><strong>2. Quy &#273;&#7883;nh chung</strong></h4>
		    <p>Website: l&agrave; trang website c&oacute; &#273;&#7883;a ch&#7881; https://dochoihailinh.vn, l&agrave; m&#7897;t website th&#432;&#417;ng m&#7841;i &#273;i&#7879;n t&#7917; tr&#7921;c tuy&#7871;n thi&#7871;t l&#7853;p b&#7903;i &ocirc;ng L&ecirc; H&#7843;i Linh, c&#7917;a h&agrave;ng th&agrave;nh l&#7853;p v&agrave; ho&#7841;t &#273;&#7897;ng theo Gi&#7845;y ch&#7913;ng nh&#7853;n &#273;&#259;ng k&yacute; kinh doanh c&aacute; th&#7875; s&#7889; 05091996 do S&#7903; KH&#272;T Tp HCM c&#7845;p ng&agrave;y 21/06/2020.</p>
		    <p>Ng&#432;&#7901;i mua: l&agrave; th&#432;&#417;ng nh&acirc;n, t&#7893; ch&#7913;c, c&aacute; nh&acirc;n c&oacute; nhu c&#7847;u t&igrave;m hi&#7875;u th&ocirc;ng tin v&#7873; s&#7843;n ph&#7849;m &#273;&#432;&#7907;c &#273;&#259;ng t&#7843;i tr&ecirc;n trang website TM&#272;T dochoihailinh.vn &#273;&#7875; mua s&#7843;n ph&#7849;m, l&agrave; c&aacute;c c&aacute; nh&acirc;n c&oacute; &#273;&#7847;y &#273;&#7911; n&#259;ng l&#7921;c h&agrave;nh vi d&acirc;n s&#7921; v&agrave; ph&#7843;i cung c&#7845;p &#273;&#7847;y &#273;&#7911; th&ocirc;ng tin c&aacute; nh&acirc;n theo y&ecirc;u c&#7847;u.</p>
		    <p>Th&agrave;nh vi&ecirc;n: l&agrave; t&#7893; ch&#7913;c/ c&aacute; nh&acirc;n &#273;&#259;ng k&yacute; s&#7917; d&#7909;ng trang website TM&#272;T dochoihailinh.vn, bao g&#7891;m ng&#432;&#7901;i b&aacute;n v&agrave; ng&#432;&#7901;i mua.</p>
		    <p>S&#7843;n ph&#7849;m: l&agrave; nh&#7919;ng s&#7843;n ph&#7849;m mang nh&atilde;n hi&#7879;u &#273;&#432;&#7907;c s&#7903; h&#7919;u b&#7903;i H&#7843;i Linh &#273;&#432;&#7907;c giao d&#7883;ch tr&ecirc;n website TM&#272;T dochoihailinh.vn</p>
		    <p>Ban qu&#7843;n l&yacute; Website: l&agrave; nh&acirc;n vi&ecirc;n c&#7911;a H&#7843;i Linh, ch&#7883;u tr&aacute;ch nhi&#7879;m trong vi&#7879;c qu&#7843;n l&yacute;, v&#7853;n h&agrave;nh, c&#7853;p nh&#7853;t c&aacute;c th&ocirc;ng tin v&#7873; s&#7843;n ph&#7849;m tr&ecirc;n Website; ti&#7871;p nh&#7853;n v&agrave; x&#7917; l&yacute; c&aacute;c &#273;&#417;n &#273;&#7863;t h&agrave;ng t&#7915; Ng&#432;&#7901;i mua.</p>
		    <p>S&#7903; h&#7919;u Tr&iacute; tu&#7879;: b&#7845;t k&#7923; b&#7857;ng s&aacute;ng ch&#7871;, b&#7843;n quy&#7873;n, thi&#7871;t k&#7871; &#273;&#432;&#7907;c &#273;&#259;ng k&yacute; ho&#7863;c ch&#432;a &#273;&#259;ng k&yacute;, quy&#7873;n &#273;&#7889;i v&#7899;i thi&#7871;t k&#7871;, nh&atilde;n hi&#7879;u &#273;&#432;&#7907;c &#273;&#259;ng k&yacute; ho&#7863;c ch&#432;a &#273;&#259;ng k&yacute;, nh&atilde;n hi&#7879;u d&#7883;ch v&#7909; ho&#7863;c quy&#7873;n s&#7903; h&#7919;u c&ocirc;ng nghi&#7879;p ho&#7863;c s&#7903; h&#7919;u tr&iacute; tu&#7879; kh&aacute;c v&agrave; bao g&#7891;m c&aacute;c &#7913;ng d&#7909;ng cho b&#7845;t k&#7923; m&#7909;c n&agrave;o trong nh&#7919;ng m&#7909;c tr&ecirc;n.</p>
		    <h4 data-mce-style="padding-left: 30px;"><strong>3. Quy tr&igrave;nh giao d&#7883;ch</strong></h4>
		    <p><strong>Quy tr&igrave;nh d&agrave;nh cho ng&#432;&#7901;i mua h&agrave;ng:</strong></p>
		    <p>Khi c&oacute; nhu c&#7847;u mua h&agrave;ng tr&ecirc;n dochoihailinh.vn ng&#432;&#7901;i mua n&ecirc;n th&#7921;c hi&#7879;n theo c&aacute;c b&#432;&#7899;c sau &#273;&acirc;y:</p>
		    <p>T&igrave;m ki&#7871;m, tham kh&#7843;o th&ocirc;ng tin s&#7843;n ph&#7849;m m&agrave; ng&#432;&#7901;i mua &#273;ang quan t&acirc;m.<br />
                <br />
		      Tham kh&#7843;o th&ocirc;ng tin gi&aacute; v&agrave; ch&iacute;nh s&aacute;ch h&#7895; tr&#7907; c&#7911;a s&#7843;n ph&#7849;m m&agrave; ng&#432;&#7901;i mua &#273;ang c&oacute; nhu c&#7847;u mua.<br />
  <br />
		      D&#7921;a tr&ecirc;n th&ocirc;ng tin tham kh&#7843;o ng&#432;&#7901;i mua ti&#7871;n h&agrave;nh &#273;&#7863;t h&agrave;ng t&#7915; m&#7897;t trong c&aacute;c c&#7917;a h&agrave;ng &#273;&#7841;i l&yacute; thu&#7897;c H&#7843;i Linh ho&#7863;c c&aacute;c c&#7917;a h&agrave;ng &#273;&#7889;i t&aacute;c t&ugrave;y theo nhu c&#7847;u v&agrave; th&oacute;i quen mua s&#7855;m c&#7911;a kh&aacute;ch h&agrave;ng.<br />
  <br />
		      Kh&aacute;ch h&agrave;ng cung c&#7845;p c&aacute;c th&ocirc;ng tin c&aacute; nh&#7853;n, &#273;&#7883;a ch&#7881; nh&#7853;n h&agrave;ng v&agrave; c&oacute; th&#7875; li&ecirc;n h&#7879; v&#7899;i ng&#432;&#7901;i b&aacute;n qua th&ocirc;ng tin li&ecirc;n h&#7879; c&#7911;a c&#7917;a h&agrave;ng do Kh&aacute;ch h&agrave;ng &#273;&atilde; ch&#7885;n &#273;&#259;ng t&#7843;i trong n&#7897;i dung tin b&aacute;n h&agrave;ng h&oacute;a &#273;&#7875; h&#7887;i v&#7873; th&ecirc;m th&ocirc;ng tin s&#7843;n ph&#7849;m.<br />
  <br />
		      Sau khi &#273;&atilde; cung c&#7845;p th&ocirc;ng tin v&agrave; quy&#7871;t &#273;&#7883;nh mua h&agrave;ng, ng&#432;&#7901;i mua c&oacute; th&#7875; quy&#7871;t &#273;&#7883;nh &#273;&#7863;t h&agrave;ng.<br />
