		      T&#7841;o th&ocirc;ng tin s&#7843;n ph&#7849;m (Th&ocirc;ng s&#7889;, m&ocirc; t&#7843; s&#7843;n ph&#7849;m, h&igrave;nh &#7843;nh) &#273;&atilde; &#273;&#432;&#7907;c ki&#7875;m duy&#7879;t b&#7903;i c&aacute;c b&#7897; ph&#7853;n li&ecirc;n quan.<br />
