		    <p>&#272;&#7889;i v&#7899;i Nh&agrave; Ph&acirc;n Ph&#7889;i v&agrave; C&#7917;a h&agrave;ng &#273;&#7889;i t&aacute;c khi tham gia b&aacute;n h&agrave;ng tr&#7921;c tuy&#7871;n:</p>
