		    </p>
            <p>C&#7917;a h&agrave;ng/ Nh&agrave; ph&acirc;n ph&#7889;i t&#7921; giao h&agrave;ng cho Kh&aacute;ch h&agrave;ng theo &#273;&#7883;a ch&#7881; trong &#273;&#417;n &#273;&#7863;t h&agrave;ng ho&#7863;c th&ocirc;ng qua &#272;&#417;n v&#7883; v&#7853;n chuy&#7875;n do H&#7843;i Linh ch&#7881; &#273;&#7883;nh.<br />
