            <p>Kh&aacute;ch h&agrave;ng quy&#7873;n ch&#7845;m d&#7913;t giao d&#7883;ch, h&#7911;y &#273;&#417;n h&agrave;ng tr&#432;&#7899;c khi ho&agrave;n t&#7845;t vi&#7879;c giao nh&#7853;n theo c&aacute;c h&igrave;nh th&#7913;c th&ocirc;ng b&aacute;o qua s&#7889; &#273;i&#7879;n tho&#7841;i &#273;&#432;&#7901;ng d&acirc;y n&oacute;ng: <strong>096 127 0500</strong> ho&#7863;c t&#7899;i email:&nbsp;hotro@dochoihailinh.vn </p>
